Package: coursepackR
Type: Package
Title: Instructor Template for Building R-Based Course Packages
Version: 02.00.00
Authors@R: person("AP", "Leith", email = "aleith@siue.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A flexible template package for social science instructors to create 
    R-based course packages with weekly scaffolds and structured learning materials. 
    Provides helper functions for students to access course materials, manage 
    projects, and integrate RStudio with research tools like Obsidian. Automates 
    environment setup including Quarto CLI and TinyTeX installation.
